,-0.04994695,0.01586180,-0.02164032,-0.01218323,-0.05681579,-0.00090603,-0.02885660,0.04576173,-0.00799747,0.09020635,0.03826916,-0.01998065,-0.05130748,-0.03966306,-0.01766567,0.02298125,0.02947405,0.01379440,0.00050190,-0.04070815,0.01066832,0.03024953,0.07079133,0.04863833,-0.01577961,-0.05956391,0.03587834,0.03151536,-0.05698536,-0.02141367,-0.06291654,0.03838973,0.05316767,-0.07774386,-0.01580128,-0.06875982,0.02459562,0.04794022,0.01841370,0.03334785,0.05824735,-0.04363072]',E'EmbeddingResponse\n\nThe structure of the `EmbeddingResponse` class is as follows:\n\n[source,java]\n----\npublic class EmbeddingResponse implements ModelResponse<Embedding> {\n\n	private List<Embedding> embeddings;\n	private EmbeddingResponseMetadata metadata = new EmbeddingResponseMetadata();\n	// other methods omitted\n}\n----\n\nThe `EmbeddingResponse` class holds the AI Model''s output, with each `Embedding` instance containing the result vector data from a single text input.\n\nThe `EmbeddingResponse` class also carries a `EmbeddingResponseMetadata` metadata about the AI Model''s response.','{"source": "spring-ai", "version": "1.0", "language": "java", "title": "Embeddings.Adoc", "section_title": "embeddings.adoc", "url": "https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-ai/blob/main/spring-ai-docs/src/main/antora/modules/ROOT/pages/api/embeddings.adoc", "topics": "spring,ai,llm,embeddings.adoc", "categories": "ai,java,llm,embeddings"}');
